text: Peasant Bloc Agricultural Ukraine () is a political party in Ukraine. ==History Партія "СЕЛЯНСЬКИЙ БЛОК АГРАРНА УКРАЇНА", Database DATA== On July 20, 2005 it was created under the name People's Party New Ukraine. It did not run in the 2006 Ukrainian parliamentary election. In the 30 September 2007 elections, the party as such failed as part of the Peasants' Bloc "Agrarian Ukraine" to win parliamentary representation. In 2008 the party changed its name to Peasant Bloc Agricultural Ukraine.Ukrainian ministry of Justice The party did not participate in the 2012 parliamentary elections.
